00:45:14.790 --> 00:45:17.570
which is more sustainable--
our historical behaviors

00:45:17.570 --> 00:45:23.180
or whatever future
model we come up with.

00:45:23.180 --> 00:45:25.770
But maybe the next big
innovation wave for the US

00:45:25.770 --> 00:45:29.970
is a global one and not just
